Invocation Name: hawaii guide
des:
A guide of Oahu, Hawaii geared towards tourists.

You can say things like:
Alexa open Hawaii Guide
Alexa ask hawaii guide to tell me an attractions
Alexa ask Hawaii guide for the local news
Alexa ask Hawaii guide to tell me the top five things to do
Alexa cancel
